text: Mary Catherine McCormack (born February 8, 1969) is an American actress. She played Mary Shannon in In Plain Sight. She also played Kate Harper in The West Wing. McCormack was born in Plainfield, New Jersey. ==References== Category:People from Plainfield, New Jersey Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from New Jersey Category:1969 births Category:Living people
